      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "AuCYzaH_3_KHS3wIEW9Td",
      "originalText": "Always check image quality, avoid noisy, compression, pixalted, blurry, bad lights within any of the training images. Upscale everything and void jpgs",
