      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "yfeAnYk6y_vUaJngP0LZY",
      "originalText": "LR too slow and not many changes or style not learned, LR to fast and the image trained is burned in / artifacts (high contrast, blurry, pixelated...)",
